      <abstract>The Western Parish was formed in 1986 to manage the shared minister between the
        First Baptist Church of Buda, First Congregational Church of Buda, and the First United
        Church of Christ in Sheffield, Illinois. The Western Parish dissolved between 1994 and 1995.
        This collection contains a folder of meeting minutes for the Western Parish.Lorum</abstract>
