    <bioghist>
      <head>Historical Note</head>
      <p>The Western Parish was formed in 1986 to manage and coordinate the shared minister between
        the First Baptist Church of Buda, First Congregational Church of Buda, and the First United
        Church of Christ in Sheffield, Illinois. The Western Parish dissolved between 1994 and 1995
        due to many of its functions being transferred to a different committee.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>This collection contains a folder of meeting minutes for the Western Parish. The folder
        also contains founding documents which outline the purpose and rules of the Western
        Parish.</p>
    </scopecontent>
